Health Check
	GET http://localhost:8081/api/health

	Body: none

Actuator Health
	GET http://localhost:8081/actuator/health

	Body: none

H2 Console
	GET http://localhost:8081/h2-console

	Body: none

Create Tenant
	POST http://localhost:8081/api/tenants

	Body:

	{
	  "name": "Acme Corporation",
	  "slug": "acme"
	}

Get All Tenants
	GET http://localhost:8081/api/tenants

	Body: none

Get Tenant by ID
	GET http://localhost:8081/api/tenants/{id}

	Body: none

Get Tenant by Slug
	GET http://localhost:8081/api/tenants/slug/{slug}

	Body: none

Update Tenant
	PUT http://localhost:8081/api/tenants/{id}

	Body:

	{
	  "name": "Acme Corporation Updated",
	  "slug": "acme-updated"
	}
Update Tenant Status
	PATCH http://localhost:8081/api/tenants/{id}/status

	Body:

	{
	  "status": "SUSPENDED"
	}

Valid status values:
	ACTIVE
	INACTIVE
	SUSPENDED

Create User in Tenant
	POST http://localhost:8081/api/tenants/{tenantId}/users
    Content-Type: application/json

    Body:

    	{
          "fullName": "Acme Admin",
          "email": "admin@acme.com",
          "role": "TENANT_ADMIN"
        }

Fetch User in Tenant
	GET http://localhost:8081/api/tenants/{tenantId}/users

	Body: none

